snippet.title: MrCaringuy
snippet.description: Welcome to my YouTube Channel. My name is Michael. I'm 40 years old and I live in Queensland, Australia. If you come across my YouTube Channel, please Subscribe too me for more upcoming videos. I upload new videos quite often, so make sure to Subscribe so you will get a Notification. My YouTube Channel is about making Tribute Videos in Memory to those who have sadly passed away or to those who have sadly died by Suicide. I make these videos just too keep their Memories and Spirits alive, as I do believe it's very important. GOD BLESS!
